KDOM Script Collection
----------------------­-----------

File					Purpose
----					-------
*.idl files				DOM Level * Interface Definitions

generate.pl				Generates ecma related code, to avoid doing the
						"internal ecma work" manually (perl script)
						Used by 'make generatedata'

kalyptusKDOMEcma.pm		Kalyptus module doing the dirty job ;)

constants.pl			Generates enums which contain all properties
						and functions used by the ecma bindings

create_hash_table		Creates a static hashtable by scanning the passed
						.cc file for a hashtable definition (@begin/@end)

cssmakeprops			Creates a list of css properties

cssmakevalues			Creates a list of css values

dommakeattrs			Creates a list of dom attributes
